{
  "divisi": "1001",
  "tahun": "2024",
  "triwulan": "TW1",
  "page": 1,
  "limit": 10
}

###

### [PENYUSUNAN KPI] Get All Daftar Penyusunan
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/penyusunan-kpi/get-all-daftar-penyusunan
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "divisi": "1001",
  "tahun": "2024",
  "triwulan": "TW1",
  "status": "pending",
  "page": 1,
  "limit": 10
}

###

### [PENYUSUNAN KPI] Get All Daftar Approval
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/penyusunan-kpi/get-all-daftar-approval
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "divisi": "1001",
  "tahun": "2024",
  "triwulan": "TW1",
  "page": 1,
  "limit": 10
}

###

### [PENYUSUNAN KPI] Get Detail Pengajuan
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/penyusunan-kpi/get-detail
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "id_pengajuan": "PNG20240101001"
}

###

### [PENYUSUNAN KPI] Export ke Excel
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/penyusunan-kpi/get-excel
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "id_pengajuan": "PNG20240101001"
}

###

### [PENYUSUNAN KPI] Export ke PDF
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/penyusunan-kpi/get-pdf
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
